title: Rank7 token
body: After 6.11 patch im not getting my rank 7 token :< i have played alot of games and the stats where good i don't know is it just me or it's a bug someone plz tell me ;/{{champion:107}} {{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}}

replies.body:
I went ahead and took a look at your account and it does appear that you have 2 Mastery Tokens for Level 7 for Rengar already!  From a deeper dive, it looks like you got them back around May 28th.

Is there another champion you thought you should have received them for?  Reply back and let me know!
